  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/67fa663a92d9492f82672171e36959ef.avif?t=1763056686\" width=600 height=120 /></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s raining baby chickens and peck-uliarly large fruits! Flap your little BEHEMOTH wings as hard as you can, secure your flock in the nest, and collect as much candy corn as chickenly possible to BECOME THE BEHEMOTH!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/a9425ed8815a8c43cc440aef455bab89.poster.avif?t=1763056686\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/a9425ed8815a8c43cc440aef455bab89.webm?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/7517c74066c0f677c4db98d0ad795316.avif?t=1763056686\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Soar across the sky, pile up baby chicks, and secure your flock to increase your score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Collect mounds of candy corn to unlock tons of new <strong>cosmetics</strong> like chicken colors, beaks,        wattles, and feet!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Utilize Very Powerful Power-ups to assist in your journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Test your abilities in the <strong>NEW Challenge Mode</strong>, where one hit = instant death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Compete in daily leaderboards for best scores in <strong>Normal</strong> and <strong>Challenge</strong> Mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Customize your chicken to be as cute or cursed as you desire…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Unlock 39 BEHEMOTH Achievements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Have the most fun you've ever had in your entire life*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/c927496394eee40e4e5f7f43ada2048f.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span>  <i>*as long as you manage your eggs-pectations</i>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.poster.avif?t=1763056686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.webm?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.mp4?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
